(354, 1, '2013-06-17 04:41:14', '2013-06-17 04:41:14', '<div class="suc_story"><a href="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-111" alt="250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n" src="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" /></a>\n<h2>"We did not Know that we could ever be this happy"</h2>\n<h3>-Mr and Mrs Amarasena-</h3>\n<p class="suc_text">We have been married for almost 25 years and we have 3 children. Our daily routine includes attending to all our children’s individual needs and making sure our family is happy. With our work schedule combined with the routine we found it possible to be good Buddhist. Although our family was happy we felt a spiritual incompletion. With EASY KARMA we were provided with a solution to our spiritual needs. Wards cannot explain the joy of receiving the offering made for us delivered right to our doorsteps. We never know we could be this happy.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="suc_story"><a href="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n.jpg">\n</a><a href="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-604" alt="1" src="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/1-257x300.jpg" width="257" height="300" /></a>\n<h2>"I passed my exam"</h2>\n<h3>-Chamindu Piyathilake-</h3>\n<p class="suc_text">Due to many exam stresses I was not confident about passing. I devoted all my time and energy towards studying still I was nervous about passing. I used the quickie package that was provided by EASY KARMA and thanks to the karma agents that did the rituals for me. I passed my exam with good results.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="suc_story"><a href="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-111" alt="250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n" src="http://easykarma.biz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/250601_4005407063731_1414355896_n-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" /></a>\n<h2>"A happy feeling in a time of sickness"</h2>\n<h3>-Sajan Peries-</h3>\n<p class="suc_text">I am 25 years of age and even since my father meet with an accident I have my families sole provider. I have to work so that I can provide them with food, shelter and education for my 3 younger siblings and this leaves me with no time to attend to my spiritual needs. EASY KARMA is like a pure spiritual gift that helped me and my family by lifting up own sprits during own time of need.</p>\n\n</div>', 'Success Stories', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '162-autosave', '', '', '2013-06-17 04:41:14', '2013-06-17 04:41:14', '', 162, 'http://easykarma.biz/162-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
